Pre-Game Insights: Moldova return to competitive action after falling just short of Euro 2024 qualification
Malta make the trip to the Stadionul Zimbru out of form and unfancied to compete for promotion out of the bottom tier
Moldova's world ranking took a hit when they were relegated to League D of the Nations League in 2020
Malta's only win in their last 11 came at home to Gibraltar
Malta's record against Moldova makes for grim reading too, as they have won only once in eight previous meetings
